      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 60.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 60.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>治大國，若烹小鮮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Governing a great state is like cooking small fish.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-060__align-002">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-060</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 60.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 60.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>以道莅天下，其鬼不神；</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Let the kingdom be governed according to the Dao, and the manes of the departed will not manifest their spiritual energy.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-060__align-003">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-060</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 60.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 60.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>非其鬼不神，其神不傷人；</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>It is not that those manes have not that spiritual energy, but it will not be employed to hurt men.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-060__align-004">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-060</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
