      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 60.5</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 60.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>夫兩不相傷，故德交歸焉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>When these two do not injuriously affect each other, their good influences converge in the virtue (of the Dao).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
